In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF James Albert FROST. No. D-2785. Supreme Court of the United States Aug. 11, 2014.

Opinion

James Albert Frost, of Washington, District of Columbia, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
